channel.title: FantasyX! Please Join My Devleopment Team!
channel.description:
[size=24pt][PLEASE MOVE TO RIGHT FORUM IF THIS IS IN WRONG!][/size]
hey guys i have been making a server for quite some time now and i would like to start getting some help, but i need some really good coders to do some work for me like adding commands, minigames, fixing up bugs and adding other stuff etc. sorry i cannot think of much atm but if your interested please reply
things that has to be updated, fixed or added: duel arena (glitched) castle wars (doesnt work) Grand Exchange (need to add) new ranks with crowns fixing the agility cape, mining and magic skillcape emotes adding the command "::mute" (currently bugged) adding commands and alot of other things
i have done alot of things to this server, ive fixed most the skillcapes and their times to go with the player, and also made it so you can do it facing anywhere not just South. i have added commands and fixed bugs, added the starter TuT and lots more
NOTE: I Am Using Corby Xevoloution made by Valentino!
to be honest. i dont care how old you are or how your personality is.
